{"tid":2149474,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)完全猛鬼手册 非常盜1-2","createTime":"2020-08-10T12:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T19:13:38.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fc4cdfa5ebdeece04a70e40338b1b1dc072c6e9d","tid":2149474,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T12:19:58.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=f361538f\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=655e1e16\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=0865058b\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-67dUcIM01j4/TML3uY33rNI/AAAAAAAAET4/RPw0Ntl2SFw/s1600/In+the+Mouth+of+Madness.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-67dUcIM01j4%2FTML3uY33rNI%2FAAAAAAAAET4%2FRPw0Ntl2SFw%2Fs1600%2FIn%2Bthe%2BMouth%2Bof%2BMadness.jpg&h=3fe66814&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/c7/Now_You_See_Me_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fc7%2FNow_You_See_Me_Poster.jpg&h=9ad94a40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.劇情是說約翰［John Trent］是名優秀的保險調查員兼自由作家，受出版社雇用調查知名恐怖小說家賽特凱恩［Sutter Cane］神秘失蹤的案件。凱恩的恐怖小說似乎具有能影響讀者的神秘魔力，甚至讓人做出瘋狂行為。約翰從賽特凱恩的小說中發現某些線索，可能指向凱恩躲藏的地點，於是他與女編輯琳達［Linda Styles］一同動身前往。向來鐵齒的約翰發現隨著路途他似乎與現實越來越遙遠，一步步進入了凱恩創造的惡夢&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2.在全場觀眾屏息以待下，由丹尼（傑西&middot;艾森柏格 飾演）領軍的「四騎士魔術師團」正在賭城拉斯維加斯發表新魔術，不同於大衛&middot;考柏菲的大型魔術，或大衛&middot;布萊恩的街頭魔術，他們的表演是結合無遠弗屆的數位智慧科技的全新魔術，讓他們能將巴黎一家銀行金庫的320萬歐元，瞬間從舞台天花板撒下，也能將為富不仁者的錢，在眾目睽睽下，透過智慧型手機螢幕顯示，轉到被坑殺的投資人們的帳戶裏。到底他們真的是有巫術的俠盜？還是只是一種障眼法？無論是前者還後者，全世界的魔術破解專家跟聯邦調查局都已經盯上這四位騎士&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n3.在智取聯邦調查局贏得大眾目光的一年後，四騎士的成員正靜候天眼的指示，他們的接應人正是聯邦調查局的迪倫羅德斯，但同時間，負責追查四騎士的聯邦調查局副主任娜塔莉，也正步步拼湊蛛絲馬跡追捕四騎士。儘管迪倫要四騎士靜候指示，但大夥都已厭倦漫長的等待，更令擅長脫逃的成員海妮離去，此時領導四騎士的丹尼爾意外收到了訊息，告訴他等待已結束，要求他們揭穿科技人才歐文&middot;凱斯的陰謀，並竊取其數據資料，情急之下迪倫招來了新的成員露拉，計畫在凱斯的產品發表會上讓四騎士復出。 <br />\n<br />\n9 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=16b01e83\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=a089643e\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9f350d39f5f659f5ef171d9b677b6f3d585426","tid":2149474,"uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T12:24:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ok.ru/video/1661048200901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fok.ru%2Fvideo%2F1661048200901&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=a079426d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ok.ru/video/1661048200901</a> &lt;SKLIVE暫時香左 直接按OKRU LINK<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/popout/thanksyour/chat?popout=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fpopout%2Fthanksyour%2Fchat%3Fpopout%3D&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=a7b603bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/popout/thanksyour/chat?popout=</a> &lt;chatroom"},{"pid":"04968ece97ea8e3296f0bbed1b6f16fbe66d9c40","tid":2149474,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9246a85f602df35b2e771bdacfbbb39ee065576a","tid":2149474,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T15:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5c2785bb602891565b56cdca9409fef9e8650d","tid":2149474,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T16:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39f5b44adc749b97c3d32fbb9a0296b8d9fe379","tid":2149474,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T17:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img